$ GCC linker option: --add-stdcall-alias

This option instructs to export functions with the stdcall → development/languages/C-C-plus-plus/calling-convention#c-func-name-decoration[decoration] suffix (`@nn`) and also without this suffix.

Compare with → development/languages/C-C-plus-plus/GCC/linker/options/kill-at[`--kill-at`]

